Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveFavour, a student of Auchi Polytechnic, Edo State, is currently on the run after allegedly stabbing her boyfriend to death.
It was gathered that the incident happened at their residence in Auchi, Edo State, on Saturday, July 23, when the suspect allegedly found out that her boyfriend, Jigga, was cheating on her. A source reports that Favour in anger, used a knife to stab the victim to death.
“She fled after committing the act and a manhunt has been launched for her. Favour is heartless because she had a son for another man and Jigga decided to take care of her and the child. It’s heartbreaking this is how she decided to pay him back just because of a mere allegation,” a source said.
